        <p>
            We are excited to announce our new holiday package that is perfect
            for a getaway.With stunning beaches and breathtaking views, this
            package will make your vacation unforgettable.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing us as your travel partner.</p>

        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Travel Company</p>
    </body>
</html>